<section>
   <h2>pluck</h2>
   <tt>also known as <b>map</b> and <b>collect</b>.</tt>

   <h3>Parameters</h3>
   <dl class='parameters'>
      <dt>attribute</dt>
      <dd>the name of the attribute to pluck</dd>
   </dl>

   <h3>Description</h3>
   Iterates over every item in the collection and returns the given attribute
   value in a new collection for every item.
   
